      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, preserved in its peak mechanical state. The S54B32 power plant delivers linear throttle response through its individual throttle bodies, with a recently serviced double-VANOS system ensuring precise variable valve timing. The chassis is structurally sound, featuring a reinforced rear subframe to mitigate common fatigue points, while the Getrag 6-speed manual offers tight, short-throw engagement. Every bushing and suspension component remains within factory tolerances, maintaining the car's legendary lateral grip and steering feedback. This is a turn-key example for the collector who prioritizes drivetrain integrity and structural rigidity.",
