      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously preserved. Finished in a flawless deep metallic paint with a professional ceramic coating, the exterior is free of swirls, rock chips, or door dings. Inside, the cabin retains its original factory scent; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since day one. Mechanically, the car is indistinguishable from new, having been stored in a climate-controlled garage and serviced exclusively at the dealership on a preventative schedule. All electronics, safety features, and driver assists function perfectly. This sale includes the full service log, two sets of keys, and the original window sticker. If you are looking for a 'no-excuses' car that looks and drives like it just rolled off the assembly line, this is it.",
